{"tid":2063413,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"長年暗瘡搏鬥史","createTime":"2020-06-14T03:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T15:01:09.000Z","uid":291032,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c4b265b4185f6dca0d009bae489a3a491ff34c","tid":2063413,"uid":291032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T03:32:49.000Z","msg":"我呢就社會人一個，青春期時塊面白白滑滑，但出黎做野後突然瘋狂爆瘡，講緊係兩邊面同時會生大暗瘡+石頭瘡，每邊8-10粒咁樣。好醜樣，好自卑，試過搭車見到其他女仔皮膚好好而唔開心到喊左出黎。<br />\n<br />\n當時試左好多唔同嘅暗瘡產品，經驗難得都想同各位暗瘡受害者分享下。感想就純屬個人意見黎嘅，大家啱睇就睇，絕對唔係廣告。<br />\n<br />\n利申我係食A酸徹底好翻，遲啲如果有人想睇都可以分享食A酸嘅歷程，呢篇比較係俾啲暗瘡相對無咁嚴重嘅人參考。由於係成日去日本嘅港女，所以日系產品佔多。以前生暗瘡時係油性皮膚。<br />\n<br />\n～暗瘡藥篇～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.lipscosme.com/product/product_affiliate16386img.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.lipscosme.com%2Fproduct%2Fproduct_affiliate16386img.png&h=148485dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPAIR暗瘡藥：應該有留意嘅人都會聽過。搽落係輕爽嘅Cream質地，搽細粒有頭嘅暗瘡可能OK, 但我個人覺得無乜用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.lipscosme.com/product/034dfec0e9a0a86ba136f9ea-1562031418.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.lipscosme.com%2Fproduct%2F034dfec0e9a0a86ba136f9ea-1562031418.png&h=3a3aa240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬秀雷敦暗瘡藥：唔係好記得個質地，基本上同上面PAIR果支一樣對我皮膚無乜用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://item-shopping.c.yimg.jp/i/j/ace_4987241148820\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitem-shopping.c.yimg.jp%2Fi%2Fj%2Face_4987241148820&h=b2c70eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬秀雷敦ACNES25暗瘡藥：搽落係Gel質地，講話係針對大人嘅瘡，唔係石頭瘡嘅話幾有用，搽過夜粒瘡明顯謝左啲。依家我都有用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://item-shopping.c.yimg.jp/i/n/sundrugec_4987103043614\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitem-shopping.c.yimg.jp%2Fi%2Fn%2Fsundrugec_4987103043614&h=cc9b289c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAPOSTY暗瘡藥：細細支幾方便，但我記得價錢唔平，搽落去會令皮膚乾。我果陣好油就無乜野，本身皮膚唔油再搽應該會甩皮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.e-welcia.com/upload/save_image/iyaku/4987415689289_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.e-welcia.com%2Fupload%2Fsave_image%2Fiyaku%2F4987415689289_1.jpg&h=6283be5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nShiseido暗瘡藥：我買果支係有色Type，勁杰勁難搽開，佢應該係可以當conceala咁係暗瘡上做遮瑕，但佢隻色調偏橙，皮膚白嘅女仔搽左再上粉底未必遮到。藥力一般，要化妝時可以用嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.slash-trading.com/image/cache/catalog/products/japan/rabbit/annasalbe-ace-cream/annasalbe-ace-cream-2-550x550.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.slash-trading.com%2Fimage%2Fcache%2Fcatalog%2Fproducts%2Fjapan%2Frabbit%2Fannasalbe-ace-cream%2Fannasalbe-ace-cream-2-550x550.png&h=e4a1d101&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白兔牌暗瘡藥：一款抽乾皮膚令暗瘡收皮嘅暗瘡藥，搽完周圍都會乾，如果用呢隻我會揀同一原理嘅OXY.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.watsons.com.hk/medias/sys_master/front/zoom/8933088100382.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watsons.com.hk%2Fmedias%2Fsys_master%2Ffront%2Fzoom%2F8933088100382.jpg&h=a6d1ed7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOXY暗瘡藥：搽完嘅位置會乾到核爆甩皮，但粒瘡斷左糧都會好快謝。但當年我成塊面都係暗瘡，根本無可能忍受全面甩皮，所以放棄使用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://askul.c.yimg.jp/img/product/3L3/8499389_3L3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Faskul.c.yimg.jp%2Fimg%2Fproduct%2F3L3%2F8499389_3L3.jpg&h=749c5177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCHOCOLA BB內服維他命B：嚴格黎講佢唔係暗瘡藥，而係促進皮膚新陳代謝嘅維他命丸。食左一樽唔見有乜大分別，可能啲印淡左啲掛但真係留意唔到。"},{"pid":"eb26d59e571bad216a34122d6e27545f649642a4","tid":2063413,"uid":291032,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T03:33:00.000Z","msg":"～護膚品篇～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://item-shopping.c.yimg.jp/i/n/miraiya18_4901417629869\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitem-shopping.c.yimg.jp%2Fi%2Fn%2Fmiraiya18_4901417629869&h=30d0bc20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肌美精預防暗瘡面膜：唔覺得有乜分別，垃圾黎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/71P2O87Bi5L._AC_SX569_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F71P2O87Bi5L._AC_SX569_.jpg&h=0f85ad12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肌美精MAKE UP DAMAGE CARE面膜：主打化妝後嘅護理，比上面果隻潤啲，係咪可以預防暗瘡唔知道，但至少無刺激到生新暗瘡，化妝後用可以平衡翻皮膚水分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://skincity.com/bilder/artiklar/zoom/1261009_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskincity.com%2Fbilder%2Fartiklar%2Fzoom%2F1261009_1.jpg&h=588652d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMASK 15：神。奇跡。好L勁。薄薄地搽係暗瘡上面，3分鐘後水洗，石頭瘡個死人頭會現身，細粒瘡會直接收皮！！！！可以薄薄一層全面搽一分鐘當清潔。壞處係搽落有啲刺痛，同好貴。太勁厚搽應該會乸爛塊面lol<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://dg9ugnb21lig7.cloudfront.net/uploads/product_image/89226/1/_250x250_89226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdg9ugnb21lig7.cloudfront.net%2Fuploads%2Fproduct_image%2F89226%2F1%2F_250x250_89226.jpg&h=ca294a03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nPAIR洗面：垃圾。我仲有支係屋企全新未開...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://jadora.com.hk/image/cache/product/168-288a-800x800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjadora.com.hk%2Fimage%2Fcache%2Fproduct%2F168-288a-800x800.jpg&h=b9002378&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美顏石鹼：洗完皮膚會乾同掹緊，出油少左，皮膚環境會對暗瘡無咁有益。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic.pimg.tw/djodjodjo/1187028882.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fdjodjodjo%2F1187028882.jpg&h=965460d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美顏水：陣味令人好high <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好當toner用，直接落棉花敷暗瘡，對細暗瘡有一定作用（石頭瘡無用）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.takami-labo.com/assets/img/skinpeel/main.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.takami-labo.com%2Fassets%2Fimg%2Fskinpeel%2Fmain.jpg&h=a4069f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTAKAMI SKIN PEEL：我覺得有用嘅，暗瘡謝得快左，無香料味唔怕刺激皮膚，而且皮膚可能潤左所以反而出少左油。但缺點係貴。<br />\n<br />\n～暗瘡貼篇～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.watsons.com.hk/medias/sys_master/front/zoom/8796695560222.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.watsons.com.hk%2Fmedias%2Fsys_master%2Ffront%2Fzoom%2F8796695560222.jpg&h=dc7f3e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3M暗瘡貼：厚度同吸收都算中規中矩，雖無大功亦無大過，無乜必要唔會選擇佢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://web1.sasa.com/shop/pimage/1276/107271504001n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweb1.sasa.com%2Fshop%2Fpimage%2F1276%2F107271504001n.jpg&h=a1e101b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n萬秀雷敦暗瘡貼：好厚唔適合痴出街，但吸收力一流。大暗瘡（有頭）痴一晚第二日會見佢吸收個啲膿出黎脹卜卜咁，粒瘡會謝左唔少。<br />\n<br />\n搵唔到圖韓國暗瘡貼：以前係Sasa買（Sasa藍架仆街咪幫襯呀），超薄可以痴出街，吸收力當然無上面果隻咁好，但都吸收到啲分泌物出黎。主要可以保護啲穿左嘅暗瘡（因為痴暗瘡貼搣嘅時候係一定會整穿），唔洗俾街外啲灰塵感染。<br />\n<br />\n大約係咁多先，多謝各位收睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af23b829555b52e78c790aba760a742d621ca4ec","tid":2063413,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":32,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"暗瘡撚真係零舍岸鳩兼麻撚煩"},{"pid":"b9ea2ca1a6801e7e632fea96b1115f024772d895","tid":2063413,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T03:39:18.000Z","msg":"其實暗瘡係內在問題，搽幾多都係哂尻氣"},{"pid":"375a150ec22f131205691b36d47d13b75fbb4bbd","tid":2063413,"uid":15501,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T03:44:30.000Z","msg":"我已經成為a酸既奴隸<br />\n好似道友咁<br />\n冇左佢就唔得"},{"pid":"7a85316c51d80af7efcf753af0ec5ba0f12a34f3","tid":2063413,"uid":291032,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b9ea2ca1a6801e7e632fea96b1115f024772d895","tid":2063413,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T03:39:18.000Z","msg":"其實暗瘡係內在問題，搽幾多都係哂尻氣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T03:44:58.000Z","msg":"每個人暗瘡成因都唔同，我身邊都有人無咁嚴重靠護膚品消滅暗瘡，不過嚴重嘅通常都係要靠食藥。"},{"pid":"1ab1977996d06eb8c89d102deec40b7d98fb6b8d","tid":2063413,"uid":22544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T03:45:22.000Z","msg":"男士應該用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad499c3227d0a391738905903a2dae62fe2b600","tid":2063413,"uid":291032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"375a150ec22f131205691b36d47d13b75fbb4bbd","tid":2063413,"uid":15501,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"